snippet.title: KnC(Knights and Castles) Trailer!
snippet.description: (KnC) Knights and Castles is an IDLE - GAME, wich is a game where most of the mechanics and battles are automated so you can enjoy making progress while drinking a coffe without having to work so hard to play =)
